Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.83,0:00:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.48,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, thanks for wasting my brilliant play!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez. I'm sorry, 'kay?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.85,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, GwinBee, won't you play beach volleyball with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.54,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He says don't trample all over that area \Nbecause it's the planned site for the palace. {probs a sand castle?}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, can I see it when it's finished?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.03,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.83,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't take this anymore! I'm so bored!\NWatching after kids bores me to death! {???? gaki no *** ha}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I’d known it would turn out like this, I’d have\Nbeen better off having a beer at the beachside café.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Won't you have one with me, Cinnamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.52,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Guess I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.32,0:01:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, GwinBee! If anyone asks, \Nwe went to that bar over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.12,0:01:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.36,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's hot...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.89,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, one curry and one ramen, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.30,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ZakoBee! The two orders of corn are done, \Nso carry them out to the customers for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can we have \Nsome beer and boiled peas? {(Edamame is boiled green peas, served slightly salted.)}{how tf is this word not highlighted by spellcheck}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming up!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.25,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.25,0:01:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there was a {\i1}big{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}sale at that store yesterday! I hear they're going out of business. {?????? no clue what's this about or what exactly she says; was: Hey, listen, when I went to Yasuno yesterday, there was a BIG fuss! I hear they're, like, in debt.}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're a cutie. \NWhat are you selling?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.\NI'm selling Madoka’s Special Cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take a bag.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go! \NThanks for your purchase.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try one right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.90,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I hear there's a cookie stand around here that's to die for!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Amazing in what way?} To die for?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.84,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure, but it's gotta be totally amazing! \NWanna go with me and try it out?} It sounds like it's totally life-changing! \N Wanna go with me and try it out?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ms. Apple? {apple-sensei}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.34,0:02:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's you, White! \NYou came to the beach too?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Light and the others are over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really? Well then, bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don’t go, White.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.08,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your timing is perfect. I'm sorry, \Nbut could you rub sun oil into my back?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.01,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This Rainbow Color brand is really good! \NThere's not much left, so use all of it, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Why can't you ever\Nthink of anyone other than yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you get me a drink too?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I care? Get one yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're killing me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where are the doctors?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.64,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the doctors said \Nthey would bee at the beach café.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t tell me they’re\Ndrinking this early in the day...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, that was great!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.02,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we'd like another beer! \NBring more beer!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.74,0:03:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right-o. Let's explore the grandeur\Nof nature and the mysteries of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I found plenty of mysteries already!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.64,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re here too?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.04,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Headband. \NI challenge you to a game of beach volleyball.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Get out in the sun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry, but I'm really busy now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you absolutely have to, \Nyou can play with the TwinBees.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it, TwinBees?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.73,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm definitely going to drag\Nyou out onto the court. Let's go, sis! {aneki}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.01,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s this? \NAre you going to do it in your Black TwinBees?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.07,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a no-brainer! No way we can compete\Nwith you unless we're on the same scale. {lit: to beat you, we have to be of the same size}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine with us! \NLet's get started already!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready when you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.99,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, guess I'll put on\Nsome sun oil and get a great tan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! Meet my imported \Npremium-quality suntan oil, Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I saw an ad for it \Nin last month’s issue of Heart Teen, {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.74,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn’t hold back \Nthe part of me that craves beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So despite my abject financial situation, {lit: and so, despite having to lead a stingy life; to scrimp and save; to pinch pennies; to light one's (finger)nails (instead of a candle)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.81,0:04:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dipped deep into my secret stash \Nto finally get this luxury oil—Venus!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.61,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I rub this on my flawless skin, I can become \Nthe Summer Princess of this Tulip Beach!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.96,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe my perfect tan will win me a pageant, \Nor I'll become a sexy little mermaid?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And... got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put plenty on, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My oil!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your purchase.\NPlease form a line.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, there's plenty to go around!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, don't be such a wimp. {lit: isn't that feeble}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really a man, \Nthen you must have more guts than that. {?????? motto *** to shinasai - I can only think of shakiin = clink; clank; clang​ - but that doesn't make any sense here; -kin also means various muscles, and that does make sense but why does she say it -kiin? also even if we assume a muscle, the rest of the sentence doesn't add up anyway}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I miss and strike the bone, don't blame me! {????? lit: if it's wrong and I give you shakiin, too bad}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.53,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Doctor Peach, did you see my bottle \Nof expensive sun oil fly anywhere around here? {unlike other doctors (hakase) here, she's an actual medical worker}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oil?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Water!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.52,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, part-timer Warumon! \NHurry up and give us another beer!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.46,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastards! How much more of this crap do you think\NI’m gonna take just because you’re customers?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.29,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear... What's wrong? \NDid we make you mad?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is the manager here? Manager!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your new kitchen hand here \Nhas an attitude problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.46,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I dare you to say that again!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oil... My oil...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.27,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I mean, it's flattering, of course... {?????? was: But I thought you hated me.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.39,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! I didn't get a chance to use even a drop \Nof this oil I just bought! My imported premium sun oil!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Color sun oil? Imported? {??????? nc what's that yakiraki}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Color? Lemme see that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Color?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This isn't my sun oil!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But then, where {\i1}is{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}mine?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.98,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It might've gotten swapped \Nwith Ms. Apple’s oil!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all hope is lost! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Ms. Apple!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.85,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,White, could you check if that oil is mine?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Venus?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.93,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.86,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's right! This isn't my oil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You still wanna continue?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya sayin'? \NEverything before this was practice! {lit: real performance starts now}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.38,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee, WinBee, Seeds, Salute. {names of those two who chalenged twinbees to a volleyball game }
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.84,0:08:07.63,Top,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! The great outdoors is something else!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.55,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, Madoka, Dr. Peach, Dr. Cinnamon,\NDr. Mardock, Dr. Warumon, Ms. Apple, White…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! This taste is unparalleled.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeds, let's try the Z-Attack next.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.75,0:08:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.26,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, how much bigger \Nare you gonna bee building it?
Dialogue: 7,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.08,Song,,0,0,0,,{あいことばはBe!! by 國府田マリ子; full lyrics: あいことばはBe!!　待っていたらはじまらないよ\Nスグ逃げちゃう　チャンス!\Nさあいますぐ　Hey you!!　あゆれでぃ!\N\NあいことばはBe!!　ときめく胸押さえつけないで\N僕らのコトバBe!!\N奇跡だって　起こせるのさ!\N\Nふかづめした朝　ラッシュでドッキリ　ベルの音\N徹夜の宿題　うっかりすっかり机にのったまま\N天使と悪魔がココロで誘惑　エスケープ\Nそうさ　ゼッタイはっぴい　PARADISE!!\Nにっちもさっちもゆかずに　ポーカーフェイス!\N\NあいことばはBe!!　教科書にものってるけれど\NBe!!なDO・U・SHIの“Be!!”\N奇跡を　呼び起こせるのさ!\N\N“告白”その日に　キミにフラれ　雨が降り\Nムリヤリツッパリ　にこっと笑ってココロに雨漏り\Nぽっちゃり瞼に　キラリほろり　ドキドキ\Nそうさ　ゼッタイはっぴい　PARADISE!!\Nあっちもこっちもダメダメ　ポーカーフェイス!\N\NあいことばはBe!!　不器用なのわかってるから\Nやりたいことはそう\Nなにが来ても　あきらめない!\N\NあいことばはBe!!　待っていたらはじまらないよ\Nやりたいことはそう\Nなにが来ても　あきらめない!\N\NあいことばはBe!!　昨日のこともう泣かないで\N勇気を出してBe!!\N奇跡を　呼び起こせるの\N\N青空はキミのものさ!} The password is Bee!
Dialogue: 7,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.16,Song,,0,0,0,,It won't start if you just wait
Dialogue: 7,0:08:50.16,0:08:54.16,Song,,0,0,0,,What I want to do is...
Dialogue: 7,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.72,Song,,0,0,0,,No matter what comes my way, I won't give up!
